{"service_name": "IBM Automated Cloud Environment Build Service", "service_id": "4760055329062912", "company_name": "IBM United Kingdom Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     IBM United Kingdom Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     IBM Automated Cloud Environment Build Service\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    The automated cloud environment build service automatically creates cloud environments comprising of compute, storage and network from an environment specification document. The environment automator integrates with the IaaS cloud host provided API to take an empty virtual data centre and populate it with the specified virtual machines, networks and firewalls.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Git is used to store the pre-requisite data files\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Jenkins manages the process of building &amp; managing an environment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     vCloud API Client automates the management of cloud hosted resources\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Puppet is used to control software configuration and package deployments\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Common repository for Red Hat / CentOS to stage packages\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Zabbix - is used to monitor the virtual resources\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ongoing environment management - using Puppet\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Rapidly creates virtual services within the cloud environment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Environment configuration treated as code, stored under configuration management control\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduced risk of manual error\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Repeatability and consistency between environments\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Full Environment clones can be created quickly\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a343 per unit\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92284/4760055329062912-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92284/4760055329062912-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92284/4760055329062912-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92284/4760055329062912-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vi\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 6\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      4760\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      0553\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      2906\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      2912\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       IBM United Kingdom Ltd\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        Christine Wilson\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"telephone\">\n       44-7809-552572\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"email\">\n       <a data-event-category=\"Email a supplier\" data-event-label=\"IBM United Kingdom Ltd\" href=\"mailto:gcloud@uk.ibm.com\">\n        gcloud@uk.ibm.com\n       </a>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row service-attributes\">\n  <div class=\"column-one-whole\">\n   <h2 class=\"summary-item-heading\">\n    Support\n   </h2>\n   <table class=\"summary-item-body\">\n    <caption class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Support\n    </caption>\n    <thead clas